_sText:
#Revenge!

--- 

To install this map, locate...

C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\*Your Account Name*\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

and drop the "fy_awesome_final_v1" bsp file into the "maps" folder.

then open up Counter Strike Source and the map should be there when you try and create a server.

---
